If you are building or modifying your own css, you can open the developer tools by using Ctrl+Shift+I on
WindowsLinux or Cmd+Opt+I on macOS to get information on the elements you want to customize.

Changes to themes and snippets will be detected automatically and reapplied. You do not need to restart the
app.

