### Headers

```
# This is a heading 1
## This is a heading 2
### This is a heading 3
#### This is a heading 4
##### This is a heading 5
###### This is a heading 6
```

# This is a heading 1

## This is a heading 2

## This is a heading 3

##### This is a heading 4

This is a heading 5

This is a heading 6

## Emphasis

```
This text will be italic
_This will also be italic_
```
_This text will be italic
This will also be italic_

```
This text will be bold
__This will also be bold__
```
This text will be bold
This will also be bold

```
_You can combine them_
```
_You can combine them_

